title: Ep. 135 - What Else Are We Supposed To Do With The Migrant Caravan?
description:
The Left criticizes Trump's plan for how to deal with the illegal immigrant caravan but hasn't suggested a better alternative. Also, I'll answer an email about the problem of pettiness in the Christian church. Finally, Ben Shapiro said something that was massively wrong and obscenely offensive. It needs to be addressed. Date: 11-02-2018
